         <h4>Help us Reach our $20,000 goal!</h4>
         <p>Proceeds will help Islesford  Boatworks continue to offer free and reduced programming for local kids, as well as help fund the renovation of our waterfront community shop.</p>

    <a href="https://dash.maineraffle.com/raffle/islesford-boat-works-the-great-duck-race" target="_blank" class="btn">Adopt your duck</a>
        

